Minister Dato Mohammed Rahmat will pay a three-day visit to
Pakistan starting from February 23.
</P>
<P>
During his visit, Rahmat, who is leading an eight-member
delegation, is scheduled to sign an agreement on cooperation in
the field of information between the two countries, the Associated
Press of Pakistan said Saturday.
</P>
