<HEADLINE> UN Chief Optimistic to Find Peaceful Solution to </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BAGHDAD, February 22 (Xinhua) -- The U.N. chief Kofi Annan said
here Sunday the negotiations over arms inspections with Iraq is
"making progress" and that he is "still optimistic."
</P>
<P>
