duty lorry was crossing. Pillars of the dilapidated bridge, some
80 kilometers from Iringa town, had already been battered by
floods.
</P>
<P>
Following the breakdown of the bridge, a number of people had
to travel by the Tanzania-Zambia railway.
</P>
<P>
