<HEADLINE> Second Phase of General Elections Begins in India </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, February 22 (Xinhua) -- The focus now has shifted to
the second phase of the 12th Lower House of Parliament elections
which began in the country's 183 Parliamentary constituencies on
Sunday.
</P>
<P>
The fate of 405 members out of 543 MPs will have been decided
in two phases of elections after Sunday's polling. The first phase
